  Locus:
    Page: 399
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Religion
---
Religion, in one way or another, has always been with us. Religion will
continue to always be with us. What needs to be discarded and thrown away
is the ecclesiastical rubbish which binds us to religion instead of God.
